{
  "stem": "18397.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 233.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I should stay, you know, live over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had-- a normal life almost, you know, in this Kylis, where they make the furs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I couldn't stay there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was there a week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The next week I couldn't stay anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I say, I'm going back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he says, he's going back too, this guy, you know, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We couldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We-- everything was not like-- it wasn't like in the woods, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Couldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was very-- I couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was a different story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother had a wife and a kid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And him had-- had protection from-- from his father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got a job like a chimney cleaner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a special job, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took the Jews, and they didn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to go and clean the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was a big deal, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could go out, you know, and buy him something what they needed, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A chimney cleaner, they went by themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What you are going to go, in a group?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he had a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when it came to liquidation, they took the whole group, the chimney cleaners, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then this man, this friend of mine, the comisar, you know, [NON-ENGLISH], he could do something.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know what was the end of him?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a comisar, a big comisar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- they shot him, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He died over there, in the-- in the-- oh, this was politics, already, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was politics.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
